OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,FThree teenagers are due to be
OL,7,Fsentenced for the murder of 16-year-
OL,8,Fold Kayden Moy who was fatally stabbed
OL,9,Fon a North Ayrshire beach last year.
OL,11,FJay Stewart, 18, Cole Turley, 18, and
OL,12,Fa 15-year-old boy who cannot be named
OL,13,Ffor legal reasons acted together to
OL,14,Fcarry out the attack at Irvine beach
OL,15,Fon May 17 2025.
OL,17,FTurley admitted to the killing, while
OL,18,FStewart and the 15-year-old were found
OL,19,Fguilty of murder last month following
OL,20,Fa trial at the High Court in Glasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
