OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784605665
OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,FAll three had been members of the
OL,7,FMurray Boys group, while Kayden and
OL,8,Fothers were part of the Himshie group
OL,9,Fin East Kilbride.
OL,11,FIn a message on social media posted
OL,12,Fahead of the sentencing, Kayden's
OL,13,Ffather Paul Moy said: "Nothing that
OL,14,Fhappens in that courtroom will ever
OL,15,Fbring our son back.
OL,17,F"No sentence can fill the emptiness,
OL,18,Fthe heartbreak, or the lifetime of
OL,19,Fmemories we've been robbed of.
OL,26,@uD@WOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784605665
OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,F"Tomorrow is not about closure,
OL,7,Fbecause there is no such thing when
OL,8,Fyou lose a child.
OL,10,F"It is about justice, accountability,
OL,11,Fand making sure my son's life is
OL,12,Fremembered.
OL,14,F"Forever loved. Forever missed.
OL,15,FForever my son."
OL,17,FDuring the trial the jury heard that
OL,18,Fshortly before the attack Turley,
OL,19,FStewart, and the 15-year-old had been
OL,20,Fat the top of a sand dune throwing
OL,21,Frocks at people on the beach.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@PO]
