OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,FKayden's girlfriend Keryn Knox, who
OL,7,Fhad been with him at the beach, said
OL,8,Fthey had been getting ready to leave
OL,9,Fat about 6pm when the rocks started to
OL,10,Fbe thrown, and Kayden had gone up to
OL,11,Fconfront the teenagers.
OL,13,FMs Knox told the court: "I went up
OL,14,Fwith him to try and stop him. At that
OL,15,Fpoint he had run up the hill and he
OL,16,Fwas just shouting stuff back.
OL,26,@uD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
