OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784605665
OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,F"Then Cole ran in from the side and
OL,7,FKayden has seen a blade and when he
OL,8,Ftried to run he slipped, and when he
OL,9,Ftried to get back up Cole has stabbed
OL,10,Fhim in his left lower side twice."
OL,12,FMs Knox told the court: "His body
OL,13,Fturned completely white and his limbs
OL,14,Fwere blue and people were crowding
OL,15,Fround him, trying to put his T-shirt
OL,16,Fover the wound."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]tD@YOUxD@PO]
