OL,3,CTeens due to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurdering Kayden Moy on Irvine beach
OL,6,FThe 16-year-old was so badly injured
OL,7,Fin the attack that he later died.
OL,9,FStewart and the 15-year-old had denied
OL,10,Fthe murder charge and had lodged
OL,11,Fspecial defences of incrimination.
OL,13,FHowever this was rejected by the jury,
OL,14,Fwho found both guilty of Kayden's
OL,15,Fmurder after a trial lasting more than
OL,16,Ftwo weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
